</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_187" id="92v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ritter <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Arnolden von Sekendorff,
                            <expan>hofmeist</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> habt, wie die hawbtlewt zu Burlswab
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> lieben
                            <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> und <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        Karl <expan>Holtsch<ex>uher</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, den Michel, <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Holtsch<ex>uher</ex></expan> pferd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, tun wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> hawbtlewt auf zwo
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift allrerst
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als die <expan>eingesloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> irs <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
                        auszweist. Nu nachdem als uns <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Karl
                                <expan>Holtsch<ex>uher</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan> hat, daz der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Michel langezeit <add>her</add> sein
                                <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> und auch noch sein
                                <expan>versproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>rechent<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> und das pferd, daz er
                                <expan>geritte<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, sein sey, als er das mit
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> wol <expan>erweis<ex>en</ex></expan> mug, ob
                        das not tu, so mag ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, daz es fremd und unpillich
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, den
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Michel
                            <expan>auszzuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleisz
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir umb
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fleiss darczu tun und
                            <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet, daz des
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> ledig, pferd und hab, die im
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        werde, als wir getrawen, daz ewch das selb <expan>pillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dunk<ex>en</ex></expan> sülle. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        umb ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. Et
                            <expan>r<ex>espo</ex>nsum</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
